com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.server.snomed.index

Class AbstractReasonerTaxonomyBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.server.snomed.index.AbstractReasonerTaxonomyBuilder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeltaReasonerTaxonomyBuilder, InitialReasonerTaxonomyBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractReasonerTaxonomyBuilder
extends Object
    Abstract superclass for reasoner taxonomy builders. Subclasses should gather and/or modify information contained here about the ontology.
